    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> onion wedges</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>pepper strips </strong>and <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-20 min or until the vegetables have softened – this is your <strong>softened veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
