            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once lightly toasted, add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to the pan with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the breadcrumbs are golden</p><p>Once golden, add your <strong>dried basil</strong>, stir it all together and remove from the heat – this is your <strong>pistachio crumb</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1664189459729-x200.jpg",
