        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>softened veg</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> with your <strong>creamy single soy</strong>, <strong>balsamic sun-dried tomato paste</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and a very generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>creamy tomato & red pepper sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
