            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained linguine</strong> to the pot and add the <strong>creamy tomato & red pepper sauce</strong>,<strong> </strong>a good grind of <strong>pepper</strong> and a splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and cook for a final 3-4 min or until the sauce has thickened and the pasta is fully coated – this is your <strong>creamy tomato & red pepper linguine</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> rocket </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
